      <prop type="x-translation-ref">月出.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>月出皓兮，佼人懰兮，舒懮受兮，勞心慅兮。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The moon comes forth in her splendour;
How attractive is that beautiful lady!
O to have my anxieties about her relieved!
How agitated is my toiled heart!</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
