      <prop type="x-translation-ref">月出.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>月出照兮，佼人燎兮，舒夭紹兮，勞心慘兮。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The moon comes forth and shines;
How brilliant is that beautiful lady!
O to have the chains of my mind relaxed!
How miserable is my toiled heart!</seg>
      </tuv>
